{"tid":1961740,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"港姐亞軍公開孖男友喺港鐵調情　網民：佢當周圍啲人冇到","createTime":"2020-04-07T03:55:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T06:14:50.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"1f2e1e7e43b2e6532ee094eb5907e7566891f6aa","tid":1961740,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T03:55:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.kingofcapture.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/dfdf_5215889555b0bc091e4821.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.kingofcapture.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2Fdfdf_5215889555b0bc091e4821.jpg&h=af72dbc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入得大台嘅藝人，不嬲都要將戀情收收埋埋，唔驚影響喺大台嘅發展咩？今次就有網民發現，前港姐亞軍何依婷，疑似同男朋友出街拍拖，仲要喺港鐵公開調情，真係唔驚樂小姐嬲咁喎？<br />\n最近前港姐亞軍何依婷俾網民影到，佢疑似同男朋友一齊搭港鐵去尖沙咀。何依婷同一位着白衫嘅男仔喺中環行街，本來兩個前後腳行，點知搭港鐵嗰時，何依婷就展開埋身攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.kingofcapture.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/-2018-05-28-4.23.56_20015165625b0bbea292cc8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.kingofcapture.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F-2018-05-28-4.23.56_20015165625b0bbea292cc8.png&h=c87161e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.kingofcapture.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/-2018-05-28-4.24.22_620507475b0bbe6ecb49a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.kingofcapture.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F-2018-05-28-4.24.22_620507475b0bbe6ecb49a.png&h=fb085009&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n何依婷見周圍無咩人留意佢，就開始同白衫男調情，佢突然嘟起嘴仔，之後又不停咬耳仔講密偈，點知白衫男唔知講錯咩，搞到何依婷嬲嬲豬，白衫男知衰仲唔即刻攬實佢咩。何依婷唔再嬲，俾個波餅俾白衫男食，搞到白衫男鬼死咁開心，最後白衫男仲主動拖住佢落車，拖咗最少都有三秒！真係唔係男朋友都冇人信！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.kingofcapture.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/-2018-05-28-4.24.54_6276769405b0bbe70a9b4a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.kingofcapture.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F-2018-05-28-4.24.54_6276769405b0bbe70a9b4a.png&h=55d803d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.kingofcapture.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/-2018-05-28-4.25.49_17993559225b0bbe8905d36.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.kingofcapture.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F-2018-05-28-4.25.49_17993559225b0bbe8905d36.png&h=8eb1e1fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92097bf2a6a60aeadf906a996d63dfb6bb80246d","tid":1961740,"uid":122134,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T03:58:02.000Z","msg":"好淫<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"690be54a0f2488a77e85f87eaf1bb97e0e8d0fcb","tid":1961740,"uid":83102,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T04:00:03.000Z","msg":"亞軍識條女都要搭地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n貼地"},{"pid":"1d2318618a151ca158554d4aba173689362e75fc","tid":1961740,"uid":167658,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T04:06:01.000Z","msg":"E婷BB仲係處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aa149364565023f108f39b332a7a365e95bb167","tid":1961740,"uid":51041,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T04:11:00.000Z","msg":"條女真係好撚靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec6f7e45370bde08b50a0dd1807f9e78c7e033e","tid":1961740,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T04:15:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ch